[metadata]
Name:Torch the Tower deals 3 damage when bargained
Goal:Win
Turns:3
Difficulty:Easy
Description:Torch the Tower (SVar:X:Count$Bargain.3.2) deals 3 damage when the optional Bargain cost is paid by sacrificing an artifact/enchantment/token. P0 controls 2 Mountains (mana for {R}), Soul-Guide Lantern (artifact to sacrifice), and holds Torch the Tower. P1 controls a 3/3 Centaur Token. The AI should pay Bargain by sacrificing Soul-Guide Lantern, dealing 3 damage instead of 2 — enough to kill the 3/3 that would survive 2 damage. Also verifies the Condition$Bargain Scry 1 rider fires.

